 8 10    Delaware               27470          154          26520            170
 9 11    District of Co…        21273           38          20249             59
10 12    Florida               563975          756         540590            778
# ℹ 42 more rows
# ℹ 7 more variables: male_u5_povertyE <dbl>, male_u5_povertyM <dbl>,
#   female_u5_povertyE <dbl>, female_u5_povertyM <dbl>, total_u5_popE <dbl>,
